Build Project
=============

mvn clean install
mvn test

How to Use
==========

Install JAR file
----------------

    mvn install:install-file "-Dfile=args4j-1.0.0.jar" "-DgroupId=org.stefaniuk.args4j" "-DartifactId=args4j" "-Dversion=1.0.0" "-Dpackaging=jar"

Edit pom.xml
------------

    <dependency>
        <groupId>org.stefaniuk.args4j</groupId>
        <artifactId>args4j</artifactId>
        <version>1.0.0</version>
    </dependency>

Dependencies
------------

    SLF4J
    log4j
    Commons Lang

